Sentencas: The performance of low-temperature solid-oxide fuel cells (LT-SOFCs) is heavily dependent on the electrocatalytic activity of the cathode toward the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR).
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: To overcome the obstacles of the poor activity and stability of traditional cathode materials, a Pr2BaNiMnO7-delta double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper structural oxide was developed that exhibits high ORR activity, exceptional low-temperature cell performance, long-term stability, and excellent chemical compatability with a BaZr0.1Ce0.7Y0.1Yb0.1O3-delta (BZCYYb) proton-conducting electrolyte.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: When Pr2BaNiMnO7-delta is used as the cathode electrocatalyst for BZCYYb-based SOFCs, it demonstrates a peak power density of 1070 mW cm(-2) at 700 degrees C with excellent stability under 0.7 V after 100 h of discharging.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Even at 500 and 400 degrees C, the peak power densities still reach 259 and 135 mW cm(-2), respectively.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The area-specific polarization resistance of this cell is 0.084 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C under open-circuit voltage (OCV) conditions.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Interestingly, the activation energy (E-a) of the polarization resistance derived from the assembled single cell is lower than that in the reported literature, corresponding to a value of 0.96 eV.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The excellent performance is higher than those of the state-of-the-art Ruddlesden-Popper structure materials used as cathode electrocatalysts for LT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thus, these results suggest that the double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxide Pr2BaNiMnO7-delta is a preeminent highly active low-temperature cathode material.
Titulo: Pr2BaNiMnO7-δ double-layered Ruddlesden-Popper perovskite oxides as efficient cathode electrocatalysts for low temperature proton conducting solid oxide fuel cells
